    "title": "Building Your First Chatbot: A Simple Python Example",
    "date": new Date("2024-05-22T00:00:00.000Z"),
    "description": "Ever wondered how chatbots work? Let's demystify the basics by building a simple, rule-based chatbot using Python. Understand the core logic before diving into complex AI.",
    "image": "/blog-images/85z_2201_w009_n001_95c_p6_95.jpg",
